  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Source</strong> <em>Dirty Tactics Toolbox pg. 24</em></p><p><strong>Aura</strong> moderate evocation <strong>CL</strong> 10th</p><p><strong>Price</strong> +2 bonus; <strong>Weight</strong> -</p><p><h3 class=\"framing\"><img src=\"modules/pf-content/assets/PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif\" title=\"PFS Legal\" style=\"margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;\"><strong>Description</strong></h3>Once per day as a standard action, the wearer of <em>ghost spike</em> armor can command armor spikes made of shimmering force to erupt from the armor for up to 10 rounds. Treat these spikes as <em>+1 ghost touch armor spikes</em> with which the wearer is proficient. While the spikes are active, the wearer can attempt to grapple incorporeal creatures with a -4 penalty on his combat maneuver checks to grapple. The wearer can dismiss the spikes as a free action. The <em>ghost spike</em> ability cannot be placed on spiked armor or on a shield.</p><p><h3 class=\"framing\"><strong>Construction</strong></h3><strong>Requirements</strong> Craft Magic Arms and Armor, <em>spiritual weapon</em>; <strong>Price</strong> +2 bonus</p>",
